- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper specifically applies the proposed approach to speech recognition, which is a subfield of natural language processing. 
- cs.SD (Sound): The paper deals with speech recognition, which involves processing sound signals. 
- cs.SI (Signal and Image Processing): The paper involves processing signals (speech) and using them to train deep neural networks. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a new approach to learning deep neural networks, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence.
